      "rationale": "Code verification performed against the FDA benchmark nozzle case (ASME V&V 40 Appendix C). Discretization errors for velocity and pressure fields were within 1% of published reference values at equivalent mesh densities."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
