      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry which shares impeller diameter, gap dimensions, and blood-analogue fluid properties with the COU device. Operating envelope overlap exceeds 85% of COU flow-speed combinations. Validation relevance assessed as high."
